_summary\": \"deep-loop-workflows is the single public skill that merges active deep-loop persona modes (deep-research, deep-review, deep-ai-council, deep-improvement) into one advisor identity with active mode packets, routed by workflowMode through mode-registry.json over the frozen MCP-free deep-loop-runtime backend. @context owns one-shot retrieval while research and review carry bounded context snapshots. Per-mode convergence, state, artifacts, and tool-permission contracts are preserved unflattened; the three-tier discriminator (workflowMode / runtimeLoopType / backendKind) keeps graph-backed modes and improvement-host/external-adapter modes distinct.\",\n    \"source_docs\": [\n      \"SKILL.md\",\n      \"README.md\",\n      \"mode-registry.json\",\n      \"deep-research/SKILL.md\",\n      \"deep-review/SKILL.md\",\n      \"deep-ai-council/SKILL.md\",\n      \"deep-improvement/SKILL.md\"\n    ],\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-06-15T00:00:00Z\",\n    \"last_updated_at\": \"2026-07-04T16:30:21Z\"\n  }\n}","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":155,"totalLines":155,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/graph-metadata.json","time":{"start":1783437228933,"end":1783437228941}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0f9540dbb0d880ed016a4d17acd22c8191b0e2bc410d31c4b8"}},"id":"prt_f3d247b83001ORixtlHi4cHLhm","sessionID":"ses_0c2dd1dfdffet6Vx3PotxpyX20","messageID":"msg_f3d245227001CSenUBt9m5EkNE"}}
